You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Mindful Walk and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Mindful Walk vibe means Meditative, story-driven, immersive. This is especially good for When you need fresh air, a change of pace, and mental clarity. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
